
Overview of adj ardent

The adj ardent has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (1) ardent, fervent, fervid, fiery, impassioned, perfervid, torrid -- (characterized by intense emotion; "ardent love"; "an ardent lover"; "a fervent desire to change society"; "a fervent admirer"; "fiery oratory"; "an impassioned appeal"; "a torrid love affair")
2. ardent, warm -- (characterized by strong enthusiasm; "ardent revolutionaries"; "warm support")
3. ardent -- (glowing or shining like fire; "from rank to rank she darts her ardent eyes"- Alexander Pope; "frightened by his ardent burning eyes")
